text: Purification with high performance liquid chromatography was performed with an Agilent 1260 Infinity Binary LC System equipped with a Nucleodur C18 HTec , 5 µm by Macherey Nagel ( Düren , Germany ) . A gradient from water and acetonitrile ( with 0 . 1 % trifluoroacetic acid respectively ) was utilized to separate the compounds .
